    "name": "開拓民クリッカー",
    "steam_appid": 3206490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/9e6ed7b977a99a285e00b065e4fec6df.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在屏幕下方进行的点击游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*屏幕位置可上下调节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事情节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位村长在村庄被恶魔摧毁后迷失在路上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >领主命令他开疆拓土。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >村长无尽的开荒地狱就此展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击来增强你的开拓能力，砍伐树木、砸碎石头、打击恶魔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造建筑，增强开拓力，开辟未知土地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在营地使用先驱力量来增强你的力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入新的开拓者，增加你的劳动力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206490/extras/0560830382ffc93985c48b215f8aa783.webp?t=1736325203\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p>",
